{"tid":1525118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(唔係帶風向) 有冇人知港鐵青衣站咩料?","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:48:00.000Z","uid":4044,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"18cf4d9cd06401c7ed0344a88b977d5453b8fd47","tid":1525118,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:46:39.000Z","msg":"(此ＰＯＳＴ只為讀者介紹港鐵車站之設施 , 絕無它意)<br />\n<br />\n聽講青衣站係港鐵o既超級控制中心 , 分別控制<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>荃灣綫</strong></span>、<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>觀塘綫</strong></span>、<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">港島綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">將軍澳綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">東鐵綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">西鐵綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">馬鞍山綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">東涌綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">機場快綫</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">迪士尼綫</span></strong>及<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">南港島綫</span></strong> o既運作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O07VU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O07VU1.png&h=54d794d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位置<br />\n港鐵青衣控制中心位於青衣站內的U5層，內設各綫車務，電力及基建系統控制席位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8AvTDJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8AvTDJ.png&h=aac46e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n設備<br />\n控制中心除了設有各綫車務，電力及基建系統控制席位之外，亦設閣樓。港鐵不時會安排導賞團，到閣樓參觀及了解樓下控制中心之運作。<br />\n<br />\n此外值得一提的是，所有港鐵路線（除輕鐵外），均是由港鐵青衣控制中心直接管理。與此之前，所有前九鐵路線均是分別由火炭控制中心（東鐵綫及馬鞍山綫），八鄉控制中心（西鐵綫）控制。這些控制中心，現時已成爲了後備控制中心，在青衣控制中心發生故障時，能夠快速投入服務，減少對列車服務之影響。<br />\n<br />\n唔知如果青衣站發生緊急事故會點呢?<br />\n歡迎大家係下邊討論一下<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 唔鼓勵大家做非法o既行為<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"08c46d664b1b825216b0018d2932d19841d2243d","tid":1525118,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"機場見"},{"pid":"48f1ccb0ed21d6c9678715c5ad1d0537c3f6cd31","tid":1525118,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"陰謀論估<br />\n<br />\n一早成班警察已經起入面啦"},{"pid":"86ada6dd0fb60dd7a5e0bb57445cdb1e33c0573e","tid":1525118,"uid":279810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48f1ccb0ed21d6c9678715c5ad1d0537c3f6cd31","tid":1525118,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"陰謀論估<br />\n<br />\n一早成班警察已經起入面啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:32.000Z","msg":"是的"},{"pid":"d77b866050706c411b6eff1afa5977d10545d2c9","tid":1525118,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:35.000Z","msg":"青衣封島<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4606fcff7aada1af3868e2af54075705732dabb5","tid":1525118,"uid":261971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL1u9jo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL1u9jo.png&h=7c86cb0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f4eba5d791498422e7dfbf792a3ed7b3dceeb35","tid":1525118,"uid":4044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"48f1ccb0ed21d6c9678715c5ad1d0537c3f6cd31","tid":1525118,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"陰謀論估<br />\n<br />\n一早成班警察已經起入面啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:50:14.000Z","msg":"呢層我都有諗過 , 但當每區都發生大型活動時, 佢地人手會點安排"},{"pid":"73c91bb3d58a29eb0d531872b1e398708394c351","tid":1525118,"uid":60398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:50:25.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524